data.description: Back on the market! Beautiful home  located in the heart of Ladera Ranch... quiet and beautiful.  Tri-level  2 bed, 2.5 bath with 2 car attached garage. Home is very bright and cheery with lots of natural light.  Living area is very open and homey perfect for relaxing with your family or entertaining guests.  Also features a cute balcony to relax on or grill for a weekend barbeque.  Upgrades include granite countertops, plantation shutters, custom blinds, ceiling fans in bedrooms, and garage storage.  Community features are too numerous to detail but include pools, spas, parks, clubhouses, tennis courts, basketball courts, skate park, dog park, community events, Sunday farmer's market, and so much more!  HOA includes internet.
